text: Zsanett Jakabfi (born 18 February 1990 in Lengyeltóti) is a Hungarian footballer, currently playing for VfL Wolfsburg in Germany's Frauen Bundesliga.Profile in VfL Wolfsburg's web She previously played for MTK Hungária in Hungary's Női NB I. Jakabfi is a member of the Hungarian national team since 2007.Profile in UEFA.com ==Titles== ===MTK Hungária=== * Hungarian Women's League: Winner 2005 ===VfL Wolfsburg=== *Bundesliga: Winner 2012–13, 2013–14, 2016–17 *UEFA Women's Champions League: Winner 2012–13, 2013–14 *DFB- Pokal: Winner 2012–13, 2014–15, 2015–16, 2016–17 ==References== Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian footballers Category:VfL Wolfsburg (women) players
